<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../039/2423039.xml">
Harris Bank</link></company>
 in 2002 <ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%221%22])">1</ref> which is currently operating as Harris myCFO, and continues providing the same financial management, accounting, and tax services for wealthy individuals worldwide.</p>

